svg.title: Sheet Music for "Money Musk"

text.tspan: Source: The Fiddler's Bible for the base, plus variations by Tom Wiesgerber
Notes: I really like this song. It's got great drive, and its musicality really shines with the
rhythm. The core of the tune is to play part A twice and part B twice, and to finish with
either the C-Part (2x) or the D-Part (2x), although some play both. Lots of variations!
